				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">SOE are working on a upgrade to the eagle eye series but just wondered if anyone knew exatcly what this was, I assume that the spell will be made to last longer. Also has anyone done any analysis that gives a rough figure in percentage terms to what additional damage Eagle eye does V without using it, As rumours have it that it increases archery by %40 but does that refer to actually damage?.
<br />

<br />
Still no hint from SOE that an auto attack for bow based weapons will be used, I do realise that there are external programs out there that can help out, Surely though SOE must realise that our keyboards are taking the hammer, Has there ever been a ranger petition for this because surely it must be justified by now...
<br />

<br />
Cheers
<br />

